madison is located at 41deg49'39''n 97deg27'25''w / 41.8275degn 97.45694degw / 41.8275; -97.45694 (41.827527, -97.456875), just west of the junction of u.s. route 81 and  highway 32. according to the united states census bureau, the city has a total area of 1.1 square miles (3.0 km2), all of it land.